Paper: hep-th/9804175

Date: 1998-04-27

Title: 't Hooft vortices and phases of large N gauge theory

Comments: 10 pages, 1 figure, harvmac

Journal-ref: JHEP 9808 (1998) 014

It is shown that a pair of vortex and anti-vortex is completely screened in2+1 dimensional Yang-Mills theory and 3+1 dimensional Yang-Mills theory in thestrong coupling limit, based on the recent conjecture of Maldacena. This isconsistent with the fact that these theories exhibit confinement.